Package org.hansken.plugin.extraction.api

package org.hansken.plugin.extraction.api
This is the API of the Extraction Plugins SDK.

This module defines the interfaces used for the Extraction Plugin SDK.

Since:
0.0.1
Author:
Netherlands Forensic Institute
